################################################################################
1. Ethernet II (14 bytes)
################################################################################
+------------------------+------------------------+----------------------+
|    Destination MAC     |       Source MAC       |      EtherType       |
|       (6 bytes)        |       (6 bytes)        |      (2 bytes)       |
+------------------------+------------------------+----------------------+

Destination MAC: 목적지 MAC 주소
예시 → ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff (브로드캐스트)

Source MAC: 출발지 MAC 주소
예시 → 08:00:27:12:34:56

EtherType: 상위 프로토콜 구분
예시 → 0x0800(IPv4), 0x0806(ARP)


################################################################################
2. ARP Header (28 bytes)
################################################################################
+--------------+--------------+--------------+--------------+
| HardwareType | ProtocolType | HardwareSize | ProtocolSize |
|   (2 bytes)  |   (2 bytes)  |   (1 byte)   |   (1 byte)   |
+--------------+--------------+--------------+--------------+
+-----------------------------------------------------------+
|                    Operation (2 bytes)                    |
+-----------------------------------------------------------+
+-----------------------------------------------------------+
|               Sender MAC Address (6 bytes)                |
+-----------------------------------------------------------+
+-----------------------------------------------------------+
|                Sender IP Address (4 bytes)                |
+-----------------------------------------------------------+
+-----------------------------------------------------------+
|               Target MAC Address (6 bytes)                |
+-----------------------------------------------------------+
+-----------------------------------------------------------+
|                Target IP Address (4 bytes)                |
+-----------------------------------------------------------+

Hardware Type: 1=Ethernet
예시 → 1

Protocol Type: IPv4
예시 → 0x0800

Hardware Size: MAC 길이
예시 → 6

Protocol Size: IPv4 길이
예시 → 4

Operation: 1=Request, 2=Reply
예시 → 1 (ARP 요청)

Sender MAC/IP
예시 → 08:00:27:AA:BB:CC / 192.168.0.10

Target MAC/IP
예시 → 00:00:00:00:00:00 / 192.168.0.1


################################################################################
3. IPv4 Header (20 bytes base)
################################################################################
+--------+--------+--------+--------+------------------------+
|Version |  IHL   |  DSCP  |  ECN   |     Total Length       |
| (1B)   | (1B)   | (1B)   | (1B)   |       (2 bytes)        |
+--------+--------+--------+--------+------------------------+
+---------------------------+-----------+----------------------+
|     Identification        |   Flags   |   Fragment Offset    |
|        (2 bytes)          |  (1 byte) |     (2 bytes)        |
+---------------------------+-----------+----------------------+
+-----------+----------------+--------------------------------+
|    TTL    |   Protocol     |       Header Checksum          |
| (1 byte)  |   (1 byte)     |         (2 bytes)              |
+-----------+----------------+--------------------------------+
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
|                  Source IP Address (4 bytes)                |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
|                Destination IP Address (4 bytes)             |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+

Version: 4
예시 → 4

IHL: 헤더 길이
예시 → 5 (20 bytes)

DSCP: QoS
예시 → 0

ECN: 혼잡 알림
예시 → 0

Total Length
예시 → 60

Identification
예시 → 0x1c46

Flags
예시 → DF=1

Fragment Offset
예시 → 0

TTL
예시 → 64

Protocol
예시 → 6(TCP) / 17(UDP)

Checksum
예시 → 0xb861

Source/Destination IP
예시 → 192.168.0.10 → 142.250.206.78


################################################################################
4. IPv6 Header (40 bytes)
################################################################################
+-----------+----------------+-------------------------------+
| Version   | Traffic Class  |          Flow Label           |
| (1 byte)  |   (1 byte)     |          (3 bytes)            |
+-----------+----------------+-------------------------------+
+--------------------------+-------------+-------------------+
|      Payload Length      |  NextHdr    |     Hop Limit     |
|       (2 bytes)          | (1 byte)    |    (1 byte)       |
+--------------------------+-------------+-------------------+
+------------------------------------------------------------+
|              Source Address (16 bytes)                     |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
+------------------------------------------------------------+
|           Destination Address (16 bytes)                   |
+------------------------------------------------------------+

Version
예시 → 6

Flow Label
예시 → 0x00001

Next Header
예시 → 6 (TCP)

Hop Limit
예시 → 128

Source/Destination IPv6
예시 → fe80::1ff:fe23:4567:890a


################################################################################
5. TCP Header (20 bytes)
################################################################################
+--------------------------+--------------------------+
|       Source Port        |     Destination Port     |
|        (2 bytes)         |        (2 bytes)         |
+--------------------------+--------------------------+
+-----------------------------------------------------+
|               Sequence Number (4 bytes)             |
+-----------------------------------------------------+
+-----------------------------------------------------+
|            Acknowledgment Number (4 bytes)          |
+-----------------------------------------------------+
+----------+-----------+------------------------------+
| DataOff  |  Reserved |            Flags             |
| (1 byte) | (1 byte)  |         (1 byte)             |
+----------+-----------+------------------------------+
+--------------------------+--------------------------+
|               Window Size (2 bytes)                 |
+--------------------------+--------------------------+
|         Checksum (2 bytes)        |  UrgentPtr(2B)  |
+-----------------------------------+----------------+
+-----------------------------------------------------+
|                Options (variable)                   |
+-----------------------------------------------------+

Sequence Number
예시 → 12345678

ACK Number
예시 → 87654321

Flags
예시 → SYN=1, ACK=0

Window Size
예시 → 64240


################################################################################
6. UDP Header (8 bytes)
################################################################################
+--------------------------+--------------------------+
|       Source Port        |     Destination Port     |
|        (2 bytes)         |        (2 bytes)         |
+--------------------------+--------------------------+
|          Length (2B)     |        Checksum (2B)     |
+--------------------------+--------------------------+

Source Port
예시 → 53

Length
예시 → 48


################################################################################
7. ICMP (Echo Request/Reply)
################################################################################
+-----------+-----------+-----------------------------+
|   Type    |   Code    |          Checksum           |
| (1 byte)  | (1 byte)  |          (2 bytes)          |
+-----------+-----------+-----------------------------+
+--------------------------+--------------------------+
|          Identifier (2B) |     Sequence (2B)        |
+--------------------------+--------------------------+
+-----------------------------------------------------+
|                     Data...                         |
+-----------------------------------------------------+

Type
예시 → 8 (Ping 요청)

Identifier
예시 → 0x1234


################################################################################
8. IGMPv2 (8 bytes)
################################################################################
+-----------+----------------+------------------------+
|   Type    | MaxRespTime    |       Checksum         |
| (1 byte)  |   (1 byte)     |       (2 bytes)        |
+-----------+----------------+------------------------+
+-----------------------------------------------------+
|             Group Address (4 bytes)                 |
+-----------------------------------------------------+

Type
예시 → 0x16 (Membership Report)

Group Address
예시 → 224.0.0.1


################################################################################
9. DNS Header (12 bytes)
################################################################################
+--------------------------+--------------------------+
|           ID             |          Flags           |
|        (2 bytes)         |        (2 bytes)         |
+--------------------------+--------------------------+
|         QDCOUNT (2B)     |        ANCOUNT (2B)      |
+--------------------------+--------------------------+
|         NSCOUNT (2B)     |        ARCOUNT (2B)      |
+-----------------------------------------------------+

Flags
예시 → 0x0100

QDCOUNT
예시 → 1


################################################################################
10. DHCPv4 (기본 구조)
################################################################################
(HLEN/HOPS/XID/FLAGS 등 필드가 많아 세로 박스화 시 전체가 매우 큼)

Op (1 byte)
예시 → 1 (Discover)

HType (1 byte)
예시 → 1 (Ethernet)

HLen (1 byte)
예시 → 6

XID (4 bytes)
예시 → 0x3903F326


################################################################################
11. TLS Record Layer (5 bytes)
################################################################################
+-----------+----------------+------------------------+
|ContentType|    Version     |        Length          |
| (1 byte)  |   (2 bytes)    |      (2 bytes)         |
+-----------+----------------+------------------------+
+-----------------------------------------------------+
|               Encrypted Fragment...                 |
+-----------------------------------------------------+

Version
예시 → 0x0303 (TLS1.2)
